{"tid":50153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<今日警訊>  休班男警否認偷$425漁具　辯稱忘記付款","createTime":"2016-12-22T08:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T18:21:06.000Z","uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3cbd39df7d408e2642a63f151cf6fdf5ff474e50","tid":50153,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:17:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161222/bkn-20161222123419684-1222_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161222%2Fbkn-20161222123419684-1222_00822_001.html&d=C9rODD4zZtdGQ3sn10KX32N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=52d3382d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161222/bkn-20161222123419684-1222_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n休班男警否認偷$425漁具　辯稱忘記付款<br />\n12月22日(四) 12:34<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=C9rODD4zZtdGQ3sn10KX32N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=941b356e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 中年男警休班時在釣魚用具店內流連期間，涉嫌偷竊店內的魚餌及釣魚用品等共值425港元，當他遭店員揭發後更疑發難逃跑，男警事後被控以一項盜竊罪，案件今日在觀塘法院提堂。被告不認罪，案件押後至下月4日審理，期間續准保釋候訊。<br />\n<br />\n控方將傳召4名證人作供，辯方亦會傳召醫學證供。被告主要的辯解為聲稱已就部分據稱被竊物品付款，部分則忘記付款。<br />\n<br />\n41歲被告蘇家文任職警員，被控在今年8月18日，在觀塘成業街日昇中心地下的「海釣平台」店內，偷竊5包魚餌、2包釣魚用線結、3包釣魚用膠粒、2包釣魚貼紙及1個粉紅色魚餌籠，總值425港元。"},{"pid":"b67f05f2f9239c6f34abd41fabe4bc0fd5698a43","tid":50153,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 休班警+1分"},{"pid":"5d6c13217a3a8a163d23ea1e0da68f3c1467661b","tid":50153,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:19:55.000Z","msg":"忘記俾錢但就發難？<br />\n同個官講囉"},{"pid":"76bcda71d5dc65dc8cd304583cece9dcd516695a","tid":50153,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:22:21.000Z","msg":"啊sir買野都要比錢？"},{"pid":"a633a98d128b58b43f1b906310edf14b9572e589","tid":5